title: Brandon Sanderson - Mistborn Trilogy
description:
The main character in Mistborn is Vin, a 16-year-old thief on the streets of Luthadel, the capital city of the Final Empire. The  story follows her life as she comes into her own as one of the  Mistborn, people who can use ingested metal particles to enhance their  abilities, both mental and physical. She begins on a journey to find out  who she really is as she fights against the Final Empire and  overthrowing the Lord Ruler. With her help, along with the "crew",  Kelsier, Vin's mentor, plans to lead a revolution and save the world at  the same time.

The Mistborn series is  a trilogy of fantasy novels, written by Brandon Sanderson. Published by  Tor Fantasy between 2006 and 2008, the series consists of:

Mistborn: The Final Empire [ISBN-10: 0765377136][ISBN-13: 9780765377135]
Mistborn: The Well of Ascension [ISBN-10: 0765356139][ISBN-13: 9780765356130]
Mistborn: The Hero of Ages [ISBN-10: 0765377152][ISBN-13: 9780765377159]

Author: Brandon Sanderson
Format: epub, lit, lrf, mobi
Language: English
